      <img src="kerala4.jpg" alt="img" height="150px" width="270px" />
    </div>

    <p>
      Nepal is well-known as the Himalayan Nation and is often associated with the Mount Everest and its many adventurous expeditions. However, this neighboring country is surrounded by the serenity of soul-pleasing temples, some of which are also a UNESCO World Heritage Site. One of the holiest places to be in Nepal is the auspicious Pashupatinath Temple that is devoted to Lord Shiva. Other prominent temples include Budhanilkantha, Dakshinkali, Gokarna Mahadev Temple, Swayambhu Temple, and Suryabinayak Temple. All these temples can be termed as one of the most visited religious places in the world. Another intriguing thing is that almost all of these religious places have enticing folklore attached.
    </p>

    <h3>Bali, Indonesia</h3>

    <div class="kerala">
      <img src="goa1.jpg" alt="img" height="150px" width="270px" />
      <img src="goa2.jpeg" alt="img" height="150px" width="270px" />
